  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dca\u0da2\u0db1\u0dba \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The railway strike is called off",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The trade unions have decided to abandon the strike which had started by several railway unions. This decision has been taken after a discussion with the Minister of Transport.",
        "They had started this professional action based on several problems including fuel."
      ],
